{"id":124792,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/牛刀的诗：写给静安大火的亡灵/","date":"2010-11-22T23:21:44Z","modified":"2010-11-22T23:21:44Z","title":"牛刀的诗：写给静安大火的亡灵","content":"<p><p><span>牛刀的诗：写给静安大火的亡灵<span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n今夜我与你同在</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n一同归属大地的苍生之灵</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n你应该幸运</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n幸运自己走进天堂</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n而天堂没有马车</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n而天堂没有音乐</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n在没有马车和音乐的世界里</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n那朵小小的白花</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n在无声的闪动</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n像要摇响童年的风铃</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n而风铃已经失去</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n只有我与你同在</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n你在天堂</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n我在地狱</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n在你飘然离去的地方</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n永无安宁</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n在不可知的世界里</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n没有沧桑</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n心灵像放飞的风筝</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n不在多高</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n而在逍遥</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n逍遥出人间可贵的真情</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n今夜我与你同在</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n泪眼飘飞之中</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n感觉你的呼吸</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n还有你的温馨</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n不知你可曾有什么委屈</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n托梦与我</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n为你讨回公平</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"http://move.blog.sina.com.cn/msnmove/index.php\">MSN空间完美搬家到新浪博客!</a></p>\n</div>\n","author":176,"categories":[9203],"tags":[]}